# üöÄ Enhanced Action Elements Demo

FormDown's new action element syntax provides better semantic clarity and Markdown compatibility.

## New Action Syntax (Recommended)

### Basic Action Elements

@[submit "Send Message"]
@[reset "Clear Form"] 
@[button "Calculate Total" onclick="calculateTotal()"]
@[image "Submit Order" src="/images/submit-btn.png" alt="Submit Order"]

### Action Elements with Styling

@[submit "Complete Registration" class="btn btn-success btn-lg shadow"]
@[button "Save Draft" class="btn btn-warning" onclick="saveDraft()" data-action="save"]
@[reset "Start Over" class="btn btn-outline-secondary btn-sm"]

---

## Complete Contact Form

@form[action="/contact" method="POST"]

### Contact Information

@name(Full Name): [text required minlength=2]
@email(Email Address): [email required]
@phone(Phone Number): [tel]
@company: [text placeholder="Your company name"]

### Inquiry Details

@subject: [text required maxlength=100 placeholder="Brief subject"]
@category{General,Sales,Support,Partnership,Technical}: [radio required]
@priority{Low,Medium,High,Urgent}: [radio value="Medium"]

@message: [textarea required rows=5 placeholder="Describe your inquiry in detail..."]

### Preferences

@contact_method{Email,Phone,Video Call}: [radio value="Email"]
@newsletter: [checkbox content="Subscribe to our weekly newsletter"]
@follow_up: [checkbox content="It's okay to follow up on this inquiry"]

### Form Actions

@[submit "Send Inquiry" class="btn btn-primary btn-lg"]
@[button "Save Draft" class="btn btn-secondary" onclick="saveDraft()"]
@[reset "Clear All Fields" class="btn btn-outline-danger"]

---

## E-commerce Order Form

@form[action="/orders" method="POST"]

### Product Selection

@product{Laptop,Desktop,Tablet,Smartphone,Accessories}: [select required]
@quantity: [number min=1 max=10 value=1]
@color{Black,White,Silver,Blue,Red}: [radio]

### Customer Information

@customer_name: [text required]
@shipping_address: [textarea rows=3 required]
@billing_same: [checkbox content="Billing address same as shipping" value=true]

### Payment Method

@payment_method{Credit Card,PayPal,Bank Transfer,Cash on Delivery}: [radio required]
@special_instructions: [textarea rows=2 placeholder="Any special delivery instructions..."]

### Order Actions

@[button "Calculate Total" class="btn btn-info" onclick="updateTotal()"]
@[submit "Place Order" class="btn btn-success btn-lg"]
@[button "Add to Cart" class="btn btn-warning" onclick="addToCart()"]
@[reset "Clear Order" class="btn btn-outline-secondary"]

---

